{"tid":1533503,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"其實六月到依加，我好想問各位手足一個問題","createTime":"2019-09-02T17:39:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T20:13:13.000Z","uid":155450,"like":7,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5ea6f108d432ec659b2a65dbbc88522b0ca35f50","tid":1533503,"uid":155450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:39:14.000Z","msg":"個問題就係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點解咁多人發夢，見到有手足比狗捉住打，淨係識影相唔即刻去救人呀？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n有人比狗禁住係地下門牙都甩埋<br />\n有女仔比人禁住係地下 仲比狗一野踩落隻手到痛到慘叫<br />\n有人比狗拉住係咁打<br />\n有人比狗大大力咁撼個頭落地下<br />\netc<br />\n<br />\n記者係最可以接近警察身既人 負責影低所有過程同證據<br />\n但係見到我面前既手足比人打緊 都仲可以掛住影 唔救左人先<br />\n我唔知係咪記者本身有守則 所以唔出得手救人？(希望有人解答)<br />\n<br />\n咁其他手足呢？次次出嚟發夢 有咩事既時候啲人都剩係掛住影 可唔可以救咗人先？<br />\n男仔比狗拉左新屋嶺番去打 女仔呢？唔只比人打 又要被迫除衫 仲可能比狗<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">輪</span></span> 係強姦呀！有冇愛滋都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />細個啲既女仔 可能咁就比狗破撚咗處呀屌！ 生理同心理一世嘅傷害嚟<br />\n<br />\n見到有手足比狗捉住 我明白大家可能會怕 即刻走開 但係幾十個手足衝上去打狗/拉狗又好 阻止下 起碼比狗捉既手足仲可能趁機走得甩 唔洗落係狗既手到之餘又唔會太重傷<br />\n個手足走得甩 起碼仲有條命比你訪問 比你影傷勢<br />\n<br />\n呢個post唔係想分化大家 而係想救得一個得一個 唔想再見到有人死有人傷 將心比己 如果比狗捉到既係你 你都想有人救你而唔係影你啦係咪呀？<br />\n<br />\n影低證據就留番比記者 其他人唔該 救人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好掛住影呀仆街</span></span><br />\n<br />\n好擔心被捕既人 諗起我地訓教既時候佢地可能比狗打緊/強姦緊 訓唔撚著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我再講多次<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">救人為先救人為先救人為先</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n香港人！加油</span></span>"},{"pid":"e19e7fd1ed0430bcc79d97ab55f60b5dd1bd9431","tid":1533503,"uid":155450,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:41:24.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"330177879a55b57c5a993bdad31d7ee76225b7b1","tid":1533503,"uid":155450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:42:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e7d50a985e301946b77a085fb2be9e307abc926b","tid":1533503,"uid":155450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:43:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b1eef6a8f36774677f6a7f23eb9aa9115c85015f","tid":1533503,"uid":155450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:43:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"78b60b64aae97a27050eda4405adbbad62c005af","tid":1533503,"uid":133033,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:45:06.000Z","msg":"就係記者堅守自己立場先可以影相<br />\n其實佢地在場已經係救人 唔識唔好鳩up"},{"pid":"b0e20bffd2c8068c9993e991c42cd9e9b045148d","tid":1533503,"uid":155450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:45:08.000Z","msg":"同我推比全世界睇"},{"pid":"222f3b1d8b076fd31fbbd83d54120468f889268a","tid":1533503,"uid":98926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:47:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">8/9去美國領事館請願</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">派人道支援/過人權法</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G3i9E9a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG3i9E9a.png&h=b678595e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M80cCFS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM80cCFS.png&h=5da9f118&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另有大量文宣推<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>人權法</strong></span><br />\n<strong>請瘋狂tweet and retweet</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3D54td2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3D54td2.png&