:32932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:47:32.000Z","msg":"咁撚on9都問得出<br />\n如果記者救人 俾人拉撚咗暴動好耐啦<br />\n之前都有前線試過返轉頭救人 但結果係俾人拉埋<br />\n唔知你救咗幾多個手足啦 不過唔夠人 救唔到係無可厚非"},{"pid":"a4cc18ec08dc1f24c8af0a4d18407a5076fb605f","tid":1533503,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:48:33.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"0b6b1f278d435718e90f00df2e3adc0e32e9e488","tid":1533503,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:49:11.000Z","msg":"［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n推上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ef914a2522738bd600e4521afc10ea1779734fe","tid":1533503,"uid":155450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3f2f7e580c1c042eb2aec73798501b9ad27bc11","tid":1533503,"uid":32932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:47:32.000Z","msg":"咁撚on9都問得出<br />\n如果記者救人 俾人拉撚咗暴動好耐啦<br />\n之前都有前線試過返轉頭救人 但結果係俾人拉埋<br />\n唔知你救咗幾多個手足啦 不過唔夠人 救唔到係無可厚非"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:51:19.000Z","msg":"唔知你有冇睇過尖沙咀美麗華條片 姐係狗捉住黑衫打果條<br />\n在場好多人 大家都剩係掛住影/行行企企 我就諗如果大家揾方法去阻止 例如掟下野去擾亂狗啲視線 等黑衫夠時間跑走"},{"pid":"c82b951b8dc3b0b077c2f9227b7c4c9f1011225e","tid":1533503,"uid":155450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T19:54:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4064c832a93a6c60bb97ae90a61b960f9edb30bd","tid":1533503,"uid":155450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T19:57:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"db1fcd8a5e4d29f19c4cde03df7dc8c6e54f0da4","tid":1533503,"uid":155450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T19:58:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">打狗！救人！</span></span>"},{"pid":"effeb5910e33f9ca18e14a80e32a50d0d6adc5b8","tid":1533503,"uid":155450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T20:12:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yKZtb5Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyKZtb5Z.png&h=dbbbf309&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n情況就係咁 咁又多個手足坐十年 大家成日睇片見到狗虐待手足 話好嬲呀咁之後呢？<br />\n幾十個人都唔衝上去救人 一係就跑/一係就影<br />\n不受傷不被捕唔係剩係你一個 係盡量大家都不受傷不被捕<br />\n依加今時今日仲有手足比人拉 人數已經千幾個"},{"pid":"ceaa1fff5b87580b75d488bba7cdb1eb8fe43134","tid":1533503,"uid":155450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T20:13:13.000Z","msg":"唔好咁自私拋低手足好冇？"}]}